{"tid":1442363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首可以考慮入藉法國做大總統","createTime":"2019-08-11T02:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:00:15.000Z","uid":2036,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e19f93ad569ec08fdcd902a64a0e11ea7ecffcaf","tid":1442363,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190715/s00014/1563128626792/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F-%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%8B%E9%BE%8D%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%BE%9E%E9%BB%83%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83%E6%8D%B1%E9%81%8E%E4%BE%86-%E6%96%87-%E7%94%B3%E4%B8%96%E6%98%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190715%2Fs00014%2F1563128626792%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2585%258B%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BE%259E%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%258D%25B1%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BE%2586-%25E6%2596%2587-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25B8%2596%25E6%2598%258E&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=c551d2c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190715%2Fs00014%2F1563128626792%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2585%258B%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BE%259E%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%258D%25B1%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BE%2586-%25E6%2596%2587-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25B8%2596%25E6%2598%258E&h=de91f686\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190715/s00014/1563128626792/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F-%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%8B%E9%BE%8D%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%BE%9E%E9%BB%83%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83%E6%8D%B1%E9%81%8E%E4%BE%86-%E6%96%87-%E7%94%B3%E4%B8%96%E6%98%8E</a><br />\n<br />\n馬克龍2017年上台之初無論在國內外都一新耳目，<br />\n不過法國人不久陸續看到馬克龍政府如何傲慢：<br />\n2018年，先是馬克龍<span style=\"color: red;\">保安幕僚被揭在五一示威中冒警毆打示威者</span>；<br />\n然後馬克龍9月跟一名長期失業者說只要過一條街就能找到工作，被指涼薄；<br />\n(林鄭俾500蚊大陸乞食)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貨車司機在facebook發起抗議，抗議燃油稅，民怨漸漸從網上發酵，<br />\n網民的不滿也由燃油稅擴散到其他政策。但馬克龍政府<span style=\"color: red;\">猶在夢中</span>。<br />\n總理菲利普在10月26日刊出的訪問中仍<span style=\"color: red;\">堅持不會撤回</span>翌年新開徵的碳稅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>11月7日穿上黃背心的示威者在法國各地堵塞道路，宣布黃背心運動的開始。</ins><br />\n雖然黃背心示威伴隨不少破壞，但12月民調卻顯示有72%受訪者支持黃背心。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍視察黃背心示威在凱旋門一帶的破壞，跟警察會面；<br />\n然後同日再由總理菲利普宣布<span style=\"color: red;\">凍結碳稅半年，最終正式撤回</span>。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍隨即展開全國大辯論，巡迴全國聆聽國民心聲並推出利民紓困措施。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(而家做緊落區SHOW 喇)&lt;----,不過我地偉大特首無撤回,無大便..因為我地唔係民選囉,8.1 去見下老解就OK啦.</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於黃背心以及一些左派人士的訴求，即恢復富人稅，他則無動於中。<br />\n馬克龍至今仍不時提及從黃背心汲取的教訓，上月他在國際勞工組織會議上，便再次承認在黃背心一役犯下「根本的錯誤」，<br />\n但強調<span style=\"color: red;\">並非政策有錯，錯的只是方法</span>，在制定政策時離開國民太遠。<br />\n<br />\n一撚樣口吻....<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/20190810-%E9%BB%83%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E5%B9%B3%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%8B%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%B0%91%E6%80%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F20190810-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25BF%2583%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%2581%25AF%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25BA%2586%25EF%25BC%258C%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2580%25A8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B1%25BA&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=5b959a63\" target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/20190810-%E9%BB%83%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E5%B9%B3%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%8B%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%B0%91%E6%80%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b61b31922b9d6e1d97300a41894e307da63877","tid":1442363,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:47:21.000Z","msg":"自PUSH 一下先"},{"pid":"1aa5f5dccd2a550caceecfd68e519f1d35fe8141","tid":1442363,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6f1fef661bac4dfadbf209d5f34d6d22858eff","tid":1442363,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1e8fa43d076e292d78349480b917f4c8f3ed48","tid":1442363,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa5f5dccd2a550caceecfd68e519f1d35fe8141","tid":1442363,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勿忘721<br />\n徹查葉虎案"}]}